{
  "texts": [
    "The classification part takes pre-processed data and classifies the interaction between two drugs as synergism, antagonism, or additive.",
    "This is done using a training set that makes up 70% of the data, and then validated on a 20% validation set.",
    "The remaining 10% is used for testing the final model.",
    "The regression part uses the same training and validation sets, but instead of predicting the class (synergism, antagonism, additive.).",
    "It predicts a numerical value for the best combination drug."
  ]
}